Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.土流壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.59,0:00:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.83,0:00:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.96,0:00:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,複製忍者旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能在此相遇 真是榮幸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九尾在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.60,0:01:08.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愚蠢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.99,0:03:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.78,0:03:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.64,0:03:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的術是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.38,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺跟衝擊波不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.75,0:03:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以那傢伙為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.21,0:03:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周圍的一切都被吹飛了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不單物理攻擊…連忍術也被彈開了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:04.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.11,0:04:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.61,0:04:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來一個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙明明面向前方的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.73,0:04:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的眼睛是互聯的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.44,0:04:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以視野相互連接並共享
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.84,0:04:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟佩因交手的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.87,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一是基本戰術
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.66,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.78,0:04:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們每一個個體都只能使用一個系統的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.22,0:05:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿那個能力就是關鍵了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人竟然獨自對付六個這種傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太瘋狂了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這傢伙的能力是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.17,0:05:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因…獨自對付這些傢伙根本毫無勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要請求同伴增援
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且必須要把這傢伙的能力告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此不惜此身…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷遁影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就解決一個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.52,0:06:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這邊也在做準備呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠省下查克拉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.56,0:06:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.53,0:07:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影分身的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候就已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在判斷出敵人的能力之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以替身和分身來應戰是卡卡西的常用手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟以前搭檔的時候完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一如既往 靈巧的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉還足夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用了雷遁影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉已經耗費一大半了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.21,0:07:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟這種對手打持久戰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:34.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我已經看穿了一些他的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.97,0:08:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神羅天征
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.73,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.44,0:08:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把所有攻擊都彈開了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的忍術看來是以自己為中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.83,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把周圍的物質吸引過去或者彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.00,0:08:56.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說 就像引力與斥力一般
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那個術似乎無法連續使用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次發動術之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定會有細微的空檔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.04,0:09:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.08,0:09:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把大家都打倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把所有的攻擊彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎樣才能取勝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,術的空檔也很短啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.51,0:09:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可無法接近啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也只能抓住這一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有個想法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.00,0:09:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請協助我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.08,0:09:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相當不錯的動作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.58,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用的術也豐富多彩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果留著不殺 後患無窮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙重肉彈戰車
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.88,0:10:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在從地面發動進攻之前就把這條鐵鏈埋在地下了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.49,0:10:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.36,0:10:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個佩因 還能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:10:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我趕上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.37,0:11:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來不是假裝動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太遲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這不是影分身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.26,0:11:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要確實地幹掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.77,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.39,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心使得萬年船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輕易靠近你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,體會痛楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到損害竟如此嚴重
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 大家快抓緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.81,0:13:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.59,0:13:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.30,0:13:25.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來應急處理就告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後的夾板就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.11,0:13:29.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.84,0:13:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來一名傷員了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.56,0:13:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓他躺在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.50,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了保護我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.06,0:13:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭再慢慢哭吧 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你還能動的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.15,0:13:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去把佩因的能力告知綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要立刻制定對策
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡…卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.22,0:14:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別管這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.75,0:14:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.82,0:14:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快…跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.34,0:14:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我…我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:13.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓丁座白白犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是難纏的傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.90,0:14:21.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 他還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.63,0:14:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是丁次嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.76,0:14:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.19,0:14:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快跑 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕僅憑現在的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.64,0:15:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要影響他整個身體是不可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且再使用一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所有的精力和查克拉都會消耗殆盡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的性命也就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個情報交給還活著的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是現在的我能拯救木葉的唯一方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.73,0:16:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才也是用那招瞳術躲過的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.21,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.68,0:16:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土…凜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.63,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管村子裡的人怎麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都是個了不起的上忍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.72,0:16:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…我會成為你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你看清未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凜就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.97,0:17:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成為你的眼睛 幫你看清未來」看來也到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:19.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能保護好凜的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是違背著你我之間的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶土 凜 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在也要去你們那邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.11,0:18:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是卡卡西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.99,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能讓我聽聽你的故事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:15.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.94,0:18:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我慢慢給你講吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.01,0:18:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴你哦 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.89,0:18:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛞蝓基本已經到達村裡所有人的身邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.06,0:19:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 繼續吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.81,0:19:21.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經搞清其中一名敵人的能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來聽聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性別為男性
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年齡看起來約為25至30歲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特徵為鼻子上有六個 耳朵上有七個飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力是會使用如同引力與斥力一般的術
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能把盯上的目標吸向自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外還能把所有的忍術攻擊彈開
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.87,0:19:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈開…所有的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過使用過那個術之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.84,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次使用之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會有5秒鐘的空檔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.67,0:19:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有5秒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.98,0:20:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣能減少許多犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透過蛞蝓將消息傳達給大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁座班為了掩護卡卡西老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.31,0:20:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與兩名敵人交戰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除我以外 應該已經全軍覆沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去丁座身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.86,0:20:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快把他送往醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.31,0:20:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還有救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.05,0:20:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…爸爸他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西…卡卡西老師呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.64,0:20:56.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去吧 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.69,0:22:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽說每個佩因只有一種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自來也大人打敗了使用召喚術的佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在讀取雨隱忍者的記憶時見過她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.99,0:23:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.56,0:23:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她壓根就是一具屍體啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.45,0:23:04.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亥一先生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.51,0:23:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能再說詳細一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.73,0:23:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一同解開他身上的謎團
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.21,0:23:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因之迷
